    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364230/extras/654bd59075d492b850dc4669850afb50.poster.avif?t=1769290108\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364230/extras/654bd59075d492b850dc4669850afb50.webm?t=1769290108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364230/extras/654bd59075d492b850dc4669850afb50.mp4?t=1769290108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364230/extras/12f0a18bc8f4d7feff2e5c185f6a1d48.avif?t=1769290108\" width=480 height=128 /></span><br><br><strong>Collect All Perks</strong> <br>The game lets you unlock and collect unique active and passive perks to use against your foes. Each perk brings new powers for even more combinations. Uncover new abilities and enhance your run with awesome possibilities.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364230/extras/c8de0bea79f63c4a26b214d73f76b7b8.poster.avif?t=1769290108\" width=616 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364230/extras/c8de0bea79f63c4a26b214d73f76b7b8.webm?t=1769290108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364230/extras/c8de0bea79f63c4a26b214d73f76b7b8.mp4?t=1769290108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Create Unique Builds</strong><br>Create different builds depending on your playstyle! Want to place traps over traps with more traps? Want to throw all of your projectiles at once - with huge explosions?  Or just ram everything down in a melee build? That might be for you!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364230/extras/97d8bd6fbc95d0adeb9b4e605cbff1d3.poster.avif?t=1769290108\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364230/extras/97d8bd6fbc95d0adeb9b4e605cbff1d3.webm?t=1769290108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364230/extras/97d8bd6fbc95d0adeb9b4e605cbff1d3.mp4?t=1769290108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Explore The World</strong> <br>Explore the pixelart world and see where the run will bring you! Use the level and for your advatage and search the detours to get new rewards.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364230/extras/1347f4af9e4758fa0c437078285ff007.poster.avif?t=1769290108\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364230/extras/1347f4af9e4758fa0c437078285ff007.webm?t=1769290108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364230/extras/1347f4af9e4758fa0c437078285ff007.mp4?t=1769290108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Story</strong><br>Pandash is a strategic roguelite that takes the player Ryu on a journey to a world where he receives support from a mysterious ghostly realm. In this Roguelite platformer, the player must traverse various areas to gradually free his world from the unknown threat.<br>During the game, the player can discover and use various perks to defeat enemies and overcome obstacles.  <br><br>Each use of the perks disrupts the balance of the worlds. The current world and the ghostly realm must remain in harmony. If this harmony is disturbed, Ryu's strength falters and he will feel the direct effects. But perhaps there are also ways to take advantage of this imbalance...<br>The threatened world that Ryu travels through is full of secrets and dangers. The environment changes every time the player begins his journey. Each journey also means new challenges that he must face. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364230/extras/cc477f837637721cb590727ba5756b23.webp?t=1769290108\" width=500 height=32 /></span><br><br><strong>Join the discord!</strong><br><br>",
